01:08:05,706 --> 01:08:07,999
You shouldn't have come
in the first place.

517
01:08:08,167 --> 01:08:09,209
Take him.

518
01:08:39,115 --> 01:08:41,366
You're really being a hard-ass about this,
Frank.

519
01:08:41,534 --> 01:08:42,575
Uh, careful.

520
01:08:43,035 --> 01:08:46,454
- Put these on and we won't have to use it.
- It's your last warning, Frank.

521
01:08:52,711 --> 01:08:55,630
Inspector, no.
We've gotta take him back.

522
01:08:57,216 --> 01:09:00,301
Frank, give us a break. We've been
chasing you all over Hong Kong.

523
01:09:00,469 --> 01:09:02,637
- Can we stop this?
- Okay, Frank. You win.

524
01:09:02,805 --> 01:09:05,765
But it's wrong what you're doing.
It's a mistake.

525
01:09:08,102 --> 01:09:11,396
I'll meet you at the airport tomorrow.

526
01:09:16,235 --> 01:09:17,694
Now what?

527
01:09:18,154 --> 01:09:19,904
How are we gonna stop him?

528
01:09:21,448 --> 01:09:23,074
Follow me.

529
01:09:27,746 --> 01:09:31,875
- Time's up. We can't wait any longer.
- Come on, give me one more minute.

530
01:09:32,042 --> 01:09:33,668
I give you my word. He'll be here.

531
01:09:33,836 --> 01:09:36,296
We must follow the rules.

532
01:09:36,463 --> 01:09:37,755
Where's Mr. Dux?

533
01:09:37,923 --> 01:09:41,342
You know, I wish everyone would just
calm down. I said, he'll be here.

534
01:09:41,510 --> 01:09:44,262
- Too late.
- Too late?

535
01:09:44,680 --> 01:09:47,265
No such thing as too late.

536
01:09:48,601 --> 01:09:50,852
Ah. Finally.

537
01:09:53,522 --> 01:09:55,773
- It's about fucking time.
- Sorry.

538
01:09:55,941 --> 01:09:59,027
- How do you feel today, Dux?
- Feel good.

539
01:09:59,403 --> 01:10:01,988
- I am ready.
- Dux, my man.

540
01:11:51,098 --> 01:11:53,016
Come on! Come on!

541
01:12:18,292 --> 01:12:20,376
Dux! Dux! Dux!

542
01:12:26,258 --> 01:12:27,675
Well done.

543
01:14:15,617 --> 01:14:18,619
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

544
01:15:01,413 --> 01:15:03,456
You are next.

545
01:15:33,028 --> 01:15:37,031
Prepare the platform for the final match.

546
01:15:38,200 --> 01:15:39,867
This is it, Frank.

547
01:15:40,035 --> 01:15:41,494
You can make history here today.

548
01:15:55,801 --> 01:15:57,343
Frank.

549
01:15:57,511 --> 01:15:59,011
You okay?

550
01:15:59,888 --> 01:16:00,972
Frank?

551
01:16:01,139 --> 01:16:02,390
Yeah.

552
01:17:34,399 --> 01:17:38,194
You break my record, now I break you.

553
01:17:38,362 --> 01:17:40,446
Like I break your friend.

554
01:18:25,992 --> 01:18:27,243
Get him, Dux. Come on.

555
01:18:40,298 --> 01:18:41,799
Get up, Frank!

556
01:18:58,734 --> 01:19:01,777
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

557
01:19:04,740 --> 01:19:06,657
Dux! Dux! Dux!

558
01:19:17,544 --> 01:19:19,795
- Right on.
- Come on now, Dux. Come on.

559
01:19:57,584 --> 01:19:58,667
More! More!

560
01:20:53,932 --> 01:20:55,641
Up, up.

561
01:21:02,649 --> 01:21:05,234
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

562
01:21:49,529 --> 01:21:50,738
Get up, Frankie!

563
01:23:38,805 --> 01:23:39,847
All right.

564
01:24:47,207 --> 01:24:48,624
Say it!

565
01:24:50,794 --> 01:24:52,044
Say it!

566
01:24:53,838 --> 01:24:55,297
Say it!

567
01:24:55,465 --> 01:24:57,508
Matté.

568
01:24:59,260 --> 01:25:00,677
All right!

569
01:25:02,847 --> 01:25:05,224
Dux! Dux! Dux!

570
01:25:12,148 --> 01:25:13,690
Yeah, Frankie.

571
01:25:23,535 --> 01:25:27,454
Mr. Dux, you fought with inspiration.

572
01:25:27,872 --> 01:25:31,458
We of the Kokuryukai salute you.

573
01:25:50,687 --> 01:25:52,938
This is for you, shidoshi.

574
01:25:55,316 --> 01:25:57,860
So you stomped him real good,
huh, Frankie?

575
01:25:58,027 --> 01:25:59,403
Worse.

576
01:26:00,196 --> 01:26:01,780
What do you mean?

577
01:26:02,866 --> 01:26:04,741
He made him say "matté. "

578
01:26:06,619 --> 01:26:08,579
All right, Frankie.

579
01:26:09,706 --> 01:26:11,456
But don't you get too cocky.

580
01:26:11,624 --> 01:26:14,084
Because you might have to
go up against me next time.

581
01:26:14,252 --> 01:26:15,836
I promise.
- Mm-hm.

582
01:26:16,421 --> 01:26:19,006
You guys are out of your minds.

583
01:26:19,716 --> 01:26:22,050
- I'll drink to that.
Ha, ha!

584
01:26:22,218 --> 01:26:24,720
By the way, next time you fight...

585
01:26:25,388 --> 01:26:27,389
...try to keep your clothes on.

586
01:26:32,604 --> 01:26:36,857
Anytime, anyplace, anywhere...

587
01:26:37,025 --> 01:26:40,319
...if you ever need me, I'll be there.

588
01:26:43,615 --> 01:26:45,616
I love you, my friend.

589
01:26:50,288 --> 01:26:51,538
Me too.

590
01:26:56,294 --> 01:26:57,794
Take care.

591
01:27:11,309 --> 01:27:12,935
He's not gonna show.

592
01:27:13,394 --> 01:27:15,812
Looks like he did it to us again, huh?

593
01:27:18,358 --> 01:27:19,399
Hey, guys.

594
01:27:19,943 --> 01:27:21,443
You coming or what?

595
01:27:23,363 --> 01:27:25,405
You son of a bitch.

596
01:27:26,282 --> 01:27:27,824
You're always late.

597
01:27:32,664 --> 01:27:35,624
You know, you're really a pain in the ass,
you know that?

598
01:27:38,795 --> 01:27:41,421
I'm just glad you're on our side, kid.

